\v 16 \w These|strong="H8085"\w* \w are|strong="H5771"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* regulations \w that|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* Lord \w gave|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* Moses regarding \w the|strong="H8085"\w* relationship between \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H5375"\w* \w and|strong="H8085"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* wife, \w and|strong="H8085"\w* between \w a|strong="H3068"\w* father \w and|strong="H8085"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* daughter who \w is|strong="H5771"\w* young \w and|strong="H8085"\w* still living \w at|strong="H5375"\w* home.
